Invocation Name: find my doctor
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Now ask Alexa to find Doctors in your neighborhood!

Find My Doctor searches best doctors in your city/state. Now find specialist doctors near you with power of VOICE!

Get Doctor's Profile, Practices and Specialties.

Try these to make your search more specific:
> Ask find my doctor to find Physician in Texas.
> Ask find my doctor to search Cardiologist in Dallas, Texas.
> Ask find my doctor to find doctors in Texas.
> tell me about doctor Eric
> details about 3rd doctor
